  Locus:
    Page: 113
Title: Stop Your Doing
---
There is
nothing you
can do,
Eckhart,
to improve on
what is
already
inside you.
Pray with
intensity
with your
whole body,
and don't stop
until you feel
and know
that you
are united
with the One
who animates
those eyes,
ears,
and heart!
